        WHAT YOU NEED TO DO BEFORE ONBOARDING SOMEONE
      </h4> <div class="h-[8px]"></div> <h3 edit="title" class="font-700 md:font-600 text-[16px] text-charcoal md:text-[24px] leading-[24px] md:leading-[32px] tracking-[0.15px] md:tracking-normal">
      Prior to Onboarding Checklist
